python3-libdatovka (0.1.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix DEFAULT_URL missing trailing slash, causing isds_login to
    concatenate the SOAP service path directly onto the hostname
    (e.g. "mojedatovaschranka.czDS/dz") and fail DNS resolution.
    Found by testing against a real ISDS account.

